- Top 3 colors refers to the colors with the highest total sales; 
- Total sales refers to the sum of quantities sold for each product-color combination; 
- Delivered orders are the orders with a status of 'delivered', meaning the products have been shipped to customers; 
- Product type and category refer to the categories of the products (e.g., tops, bottoms, dresses) and the subcategories within those categories.
